# onnx-diff
A tool to find differences between [ONNX](https://github.com/onnx/onnx) files.

## Develop
Build and install:
```
poetry install
```

Run:
```
poetry run python onnx_diff/diff.py </path/to/a.onnx> </path/to/b.onnx>
```

Test:
```
poetry run pytest -s
```
